{
  "id": "adv_bond_mei_01_04",
  "title": "早坂芽衣4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふんふ～ん\nお皿をごっしごっし、コップをキュッキュ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ hmm‚ hm~mm\nScrub-scrub the plates‚ squeak-squeak the cups~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7066.6666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、明日のスケジュールなんだけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ about tomorrow's schedule――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_break-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.6660944
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ！？\n大変、沙季ちゃんのお茶碗、割っちゃった……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whaah!?\nOh no‚ I broke Saki-chan's bowl…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8333327611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん、洗い物してる時に！　怪我してない？\n沙季には、私も一緒に謝るから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ you were doing the dishes! Are you hurt?\nI'll apologize to Saki too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、急いで買いに行かないと\n沙季ちゃんがご飯食べられなくなっちゃう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ if we don't hurry up and go shopping‚\nSaki-chan won't be able to eat…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7333304088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "他の食器を使えば大丈夫だと思うけど……\nそうね、沙季へのお詫びに、二人で買いに行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it'll be fine if she uses a different bowl…\nFine‚ let's go shopping together and apologize to Saki",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7999965032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.5833283107
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんのお茶碗、どれがいいかなぁ？\nあ！　この猫ちゃんのお茶碗、可愛い～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki's bowl‚ which one is better?\nOh! This cat bowl‚ so cute~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.6333283107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.8097749464
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.1999949773
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "確かに可愛いけど、沙季のなんだから\n沙季が気に入ってくれそうなのを選ばないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's surely cute‚ but it's Saki's bowl\nWe have to choose something Saki would like",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1999949773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.4333283107
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんが気に入ってくれそうなの……\nうーん、千紗ちゃんのお茶碗があったらな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What Saki-chan would like is…\nUmmー‚ If I have a Chisa's face bowl~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4333283107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.7999949773
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗の顔がプリントされてるのかしら……？\nアイドルのグッズでお茶碗ってあんまりないと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that Chisa's face printed on it…?\nI don't think there are many bowls among idol goods",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7999949773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7666585922
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、沙季が前に使ってたお茶碗って\n無地のシンプルなものだったし、こういうのでも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ the bowl Saki used before\nwas plain and simple‚ and this too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7666585922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.1333252589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "……！\n琴乃ちゃん、これ！　この猫ちゃんのにしようよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!\nKotono-chan‚ this! Let's get this cat one!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1333252589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.0999919255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、だから猫ちゃんのは、芽衣が好きなやつで……\n……あ……この、帽子を被ってる猫って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ so the cat one is one you like…\n…Ah …this‚ cat wearing a hat…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.0999919255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.3003608771
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.3333252589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんが好きなキャラクターだったよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's Saki's favorite character‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3333252589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.8999919255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうね。何回見ても、なんとも言えない\nデザインだけど……これなら喜んでくれるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes‚ No matter how many times I look at it‚ it's a design that\nleaves me speechless… I think she'll like this one",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふんふ～ん\nお箸をごっしごっし、お茶碗キュッキュ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ hmm‚ hm~mm\nScrub-scrub the chopsticks‚ squeak-squeak the cups~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.5999919255,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7000
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、芽衣。この間のライブなんだけど……\nって、ごめん。洗い物、邪魔しちゃ悪いわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Mei‚ It's about the live a few days ago…\nOh‚ sorry‚ Don't disturb the dishes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.5999919255,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_break-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13083.849712800004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ～。もう割っちゃったりしない――\nわああああ！？　莉央ちゃんのお茶碗、割っちゃった！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine~‚ I don't break anything anymore――\nWhaaaah!? I broke Rio-san's bowl!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5666585922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう！？\nまたあの猫ちゃんのお茶碗、買いに行かないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do!?\nI have to go buy that cat bowl again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.166653506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_04-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "め、芽衣、あれは沙季だから喜んでただけで……\nとりあえず、一緒に割れた破片、片付けよっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-Mei‚ she was only happy because it was Saki…\nFor now‚ let's clean up the broken pieces‚ together",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.766653506,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}